      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this dependable ride! This car is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a great price. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its adventures, it remains a reliable choice that\u2019s ready for many more miles. It\u2019s an enthusiastic pick for anyone who values practicality and character!",
