    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed on a monthly basis. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to ensure long-term protection; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The original alloy wheels are flawless, free of any curb rash, and wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather upholstery is supple and shows no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation interface, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively by factory-certified technicians. The engine bay is meticulously clean, showing no signs of fluid seepage or aging. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine collector-grade vehicle that smells, looks, and drives like new. Serious inquiries are invited for a personal inspection to verify the uncompromising quality of this machine.",
